<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Terms & Conditions | Shortly</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Terms & Conditions Styles */
        .terms-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .terms-header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f2f5;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .terms-title {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .last-updated {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .terms-section {
            margin: 2.5rem 0;
        }

        .terms-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1e90ff;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .terms-section p {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .terms-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border-left: 3px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .terms-list li {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: #f8fafc;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .terms-list li:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }

        .contact-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .contact-link {
            color: #1e90ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .contact-link:hover {
            color: #0b6cda;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .terms-container {
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .terms-title {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }

            .terms-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }

            .terms-list li {
                padding: 0.75rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <div class="terms-container">
                <div class="terms-header">
                    <h1 class="terms-title">Terms & Conditions</h1>
                    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 7, 2025</p>
                    <p>Welcome to Shortly! Please read these Terms carefully before using our services.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>1. Use of Service</h2>
                    <p>Shortly provides URL shortening services. You agree to use our platform responsibly and lawfully.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="terms-list">
                        <li>No spamming or unsolicited messaging</li>
                        <li>No harmful or illegal redirects</li>
                        <li>Compliance with all applicable laws</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>2. Account Responsibility</h2>
                    <p>You are responsible for maintaining account security and all activities under your account.
                        Promptly report any unauthorized access.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
                    <p>All Shortly content and features are protected intellectual property. Unauthorized use or
                        distribution is prohibited.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>4. Termination</h2>
                    <p>We reserve the right to terminate access for Terms violations or service misuse without notice.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>5. Disclaimer</h2>
                    <p>Services provided "as-is" without warranties. We don't guarantee uninterrupted service or link
                        accuracy.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                    <p>We're not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages from service use.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>7. Changes to Terms</h2>
                    <p>Terms may be updated periodically. Continued use constitutes acceptance of revised Terms.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="terms-section">
                    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact our support team:</p>
                        <a href="mailto:support@shortly.com" class="contact-link">support@shortly.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>